doc.after: The terminology of a superpower is not clearly defined and as a consequence they may differ between sources 1 However a fundamental characteristic that is consistent with all definitions of a superpower is a nation or state that has mastered the seven dimensions of state power geography population economy resources military diplomacy and national identity 4
